   <S PAR='90' RSNT='1' SNO='90'>This phrase does not mean to teach accidentally.</S>
   <S PAR='91' RSNT='1' SNO='91'>It is to teach in a habitual way.</S>
   <S PAR='92' RSNT='1' SNO='92'>Apt to teach implies a habit, a desire, or an appetite to teach.</S>
