   <S PAR='136' RSNT='1' SNO='136'>This is why I say strongly that we need a change in our system.</S>
   <S PAR='137' RSNT='1' SNO='137'>Our present practice is mainly to give a message.</S>
   <S PAR='138' RSNT='1' SNO='138'>A message at the most could only stir you up, affording you some inspiration.</S>
   <S PAR='139' RSNT='1' SNO='139'>Such a meeting is not an educational matter.</S>
