   <S PAR='208' RSNT='1' SNO='208'>The entire church is stirred up, charged with something to do.</S>
   <S PAR='209' RSNT='1' SNO='209'>Thus far I have only received confirming reports that these small group meetings do work.</S>
   <S PAR='210' RSNT='1' SNO='210'>Now I am waiting to hear how they labor in the Word and labor in teaching.</S>
   <S PAR='211' RSNT='1' SNO='211'>In the home the mother should cook and teach.</S>
   <S PAR='212' RSNT='1' SNO='212'>This is on her side.</S>
   <S PAR='213' RSNT='1' SNO='213'>On the children s side, they have to eat properly and must learn to study properly.</S>
   <S PAR='214' RSNT='1' SNO='214'>I believe as long as you have a good, diligent mother doing the proper cooking and teaching, most of the children will cooperate with her.</S>
